channel.topic:
Build and market a house fit for a witch!
Challenge dates: October 20, 2020 – November 2, 2020 at 6 PM PT

messages.content:
🧙‍♀️ **Witch Hut Build Challenge!** 🧹

This season, the spookiest of seasons, witches are moving in! Fear not, for they are on a hunt… for a hut and you are a house seller!

Your job: **Build and market a house fit for a witch!** 

Which witch will willingly want your spooky abode? WhoOoooo knows… but we’re all tuned in and excited to see what sells and what’s squat! Let’s see some brewtiful witch huts! ⚗️

:timer: Challenge dates: October 20, 2020 – November 2, 2020 at 6 PM PT

__Challenge Guidelines__
:earth: Your creation must be built entirely by you and in Minecraft Earth.
:crafting_table: Your build must be a brand new creation, crafted just for this challenge.
:buildplate: Build your imagination! The challenge theme is open to interpretation.
:sign: Post images or a video __and__ buildplate link of your one (1) final submission in #witch-hut-challenge by the end date. Feel free to ask a Moderator to pin it!
:challenges_og: Submissions may be featured in social media posts.
👻 Have fun!
